\n\n13. Now let's reflect on clue 12; iterate its digits until you scoop out a single digit. What does this distilled number represent?\n\n14. In the pursuit of gold, one fencer shined brightly. How many Olympic gold medals did this illustrious figure, connected to fencing, earn in his lifetime?\n\n15. Tread softly through the pages of history to uncover how many Olympic Games a fencer by the name Mihai Țiu contested. What number shall you find?\n\n16. Among those who fought with swords, another transitioned to a celebrated club. In which year did Iuliu Falb make his shift to this famed institution?\n\n17. Finally, calculate the digital root of the sum achieved by adding the findings from clues 8, 12, and 16. What single digit emerges from this computation?",
